In case anyone else is interested, here is the REST API to decommission a component instance (aka container):

 
{code:java}
PUT  /app/v1/services/{service_name}

{
  "components" : 
    [
      {
        "name": "{component_name}",
        "decommissioned_instances": ["{component_instance_name}"]
      }
    ]
}{code}

